wminc-custom-editnotice-2: Ki he fakahā o te 'u lea e ke poto ai, faka'aoga te $1. O hage lā, e ke lea fakafalani koe kae e ke poto lelei i te fakapilitania, faka'aoga te $2.
wminc-custom-featuredwikis-approved: Kua fakamo'oni pea/pe fakatu'u te 'u gaue aeni:
wminc-custom-featuredwikis-active: Ko te 'u gaue aeni e lolotoga pea e lagi ma'u vave nai 'anātou 'u site:
wminc-custom-featuredwikis-permanent: Ko te 'u gaue aeni e lagi tuku ia i heni:
wminc-custom-newarticletext-noprefix: Fakatokaga: E ke fa'u nei te pāsina e hala mo he [[$1|fakamu'a]].
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-3: E ke fa'u nei te pāsina fo'ou e ([[$1|mu'akupu]]) e higoa ko "{{FULLPAGENAME}}".
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-title: E ke fakatu'u nei he pāsina e hala tana higoa.
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-text:
E hala i te higoa te [[$1|mu'akupu]] pe ko tana fa'ahiga tohi.

Kā ne'e ke kaku mai ki heni mai he tahi pāsina, liliu ki ai o fetogi te tāpiki pea toe fakahigoa fakalelei te pāsina. Kā e ke fia fa'u fakahagatonu te pāsina pea tohi fakalelei tona higoa.

Kā mole lava fa'u e koe he pāsina fo'ou, 'uhi ko te koga aeni e tuha mo tona higoa, faitohi mai ki te [[$2|pule gaue]].
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-title: E ke faiga'i nei ke fa'u he pāsina fo'ou kae e mole lelei tona [[$1|nūmelo ISO 639-1 pe -3]].
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-text:
Ko te nūmelo aeni e lagi hala pe mole pipiki i he lea e tali i te 'u gaue o te Vikimetia.

Kā ne'e ke kaku mai ki heni mai he tahi pāsina, liliu ki ai o fetogi te fakapipiki pea fa'u mo he pāsina fo'ou aki he higoa e tonu.

Kā mole lava fa'u e koe he pāsina fo'ou, 'uhi ko te koga aeni, faitohi mai ki te [[$1|pule gaue]].
wminc-custom-tb-space-colon: E hala te tohi o te higoa he ma'ua ke kamata aki he kupu.
wminc-gadget-addprefix-help: Mole ma'ua ke faka'aoga'i he mu'akupu mo kā e fetogi te pāsina aeni. E tohi fakahagatonu pe ia mo kā faka'asi te pāsina.
